SELECT "CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT"."COUNTRY_ID", "MD_COUNTRY"."COUNTRY_NAME_TH", "MD_COUNTRY"."COUNTRY_NAME_EN", SUM(CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT.SUM) AS NUM FROM "CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT" JOIN "MD_COUNTRY" ON "MD_COUNTRY"."COUNTRYID" = "CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT"."COUNTRY_ID" JOIN "MD_PORT" ON "MD_PORT"."PORT_ID" = "CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT"."OFFICE_ID" AND "PORT_CATEGORY_ID" = 1 WHERE TO_CHAR( CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT.REPORT_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') = '2023-04-25' GROUP BY "CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT"."COUNTRY_ID", "MD_COUNTRY"."COUNTRY_NAME_TH", "MD_COUNTRY"."COUNTRY_NAME_EN" ORDER BY "NUM" DESC

SELECT "CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT"."OFFICE_ID", "MD_PORT"."PORT_NAME", "MD_PORT"."PORT_TYPE", SUM(CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT.SUM) AS NUM FROM "CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT" JOIN "MD_PORT" ON "MD_PORT"."PORT_ID" = "CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT"."OFFICE_ID" AND "PORT_CATEGORY_ID" = 1 WHERE "REPORT_DATE" BETWEEN TO_DATE('2023-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD') AND TO_DATE('2023-04-25','YYYY-MM-DD') GROUP BY "CAL_SUM_DATA_REPORT"."OFFICE_ID", "MD_PORT"."PORT_NAME", "MD_PORT"."PORT_TYPE" ORDER BY "NUM" DESC
